    "Section 2 introduces the LWE problem and its algebraic variants used in FHE schemes.",
    "Section 3 discusses several security notions relevant to protocols making use of FHE.",
    "Section 4 states the security levels that we target and describes the tools and assumptions that we use to give concrete security estimates of LWE parameter sets.",
    "Section 5.1 gives examples of LWE parameter sets chosen to target a given security level that can be used in FHE applications.",
    "Section 5.2 presents examples of complete FHE parameter sets."
